{"tid":1550724,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽 日 唔 好 食 糖 水 OK ？","createTime":"2019-09-07T17:20:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T17:33:57.000Z","uid":151256,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4024c82ced1a4f3696c6a824f6dc0d9fd724bcc5","tid":1550724,"uid":151256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:20:34.000Z","msg":"由6 9開始話要同港共攪炒，而家終於有少少進展，聽日我求你哋唔好食糖水。<br />\n<br />\n你夜晚去食糖水，夜晚活動嘅聲浪就會蓋過中午嘅美領遊行集會。<br />\n<br />\n雖然聽日好近柒婆屋企，但大家忍一忍手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽日主題係民主人權法案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不衝擊，不塗鴉，全日和理優<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n夜晚有糖水食嘅話，好大機會會將後日headline變人狗大混戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"371457b68dbb03f92186f19d388b8f3b0d08c9ce","tid":1550724,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:21:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"04beb82e4daa3a1409c89afc9072b08068d7315c","tid":1550724,"uid":151256,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:21:55.000Z","msg":"不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射<br />\n<br />\n聽日係捉鬼好機會呀"},{"pid":"7d064875f8b9fd287d4230e26e3fe5905b0be954","tid":1550724,"uid":151256,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:24:03.000Z","msg":"聽日得一個主題架咋！太子站你哋星期一再去啦"},{"pid":"03400373561266093cb1442d41b5731531498add","tid":1550724,"uid":198770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:24:35.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1487c7d3bec743ce8b2fad1b5b1e3777d5362032","tid":1550724,"uid":157891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:25:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dcd7f6e8beb789af6a871ff9cfe4ab64bf038c79","tid":1550724,"uid":174663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:25:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5cad3c0566b90e0fc9fbab3690531e5c985f47df","tid":1550724,"uid":151256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:26:46.000Z","msg":"大家聽日可以決定美國電視台點報導我哋，好好利用免費文宣機會呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d09197f401d14e6592bbd52403ff7d9146778b4d","tid":1550724,"uid":110043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:27:26.000Z","msg":"聽日忍手呀"},{"pid":"1ae8eddb5d649490381fe2dbbdb229ad4cc56b02","tid":1550724,"uid":37922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:27:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0e80cd6874ba7200aaab40731f5f533b916ab8c0","tid":1550724,"uid":217270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:27:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ef68e0f03ac2d169d236bdaaaa7da4fee5a503c8","tid":1550724,"uid":27411,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:29:14.000Z","msg":"大家忍一忍，去完就返屋企同屋企人食飯ok?"},{"pid":"26038bd1093fb5c83377556d95e0b8c828debf08","tid":1550724,"uid":151256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef68e0f03ac2d169d236bdaaaa7da4fee5a503c8","tid":1550724,"uid":27411,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:29:14.000Z","ms